commit.message: Build fixes patch from Ozkan Sezer
Added header files
More xdelta cleanup from Ozkan Sezer

Merged in patches from Ozkan Sezer:
- GCC 4.0 fixes
- Use xdelta 1.1.3 (patches included)
- Renamed base dir from data to patchdata
- Detect applied patches
AMD64 support
Respect amd64 systems in the patch startup script.
Merged patch from John Quigley
Updated.
Patched to handle new versions of ls.
Fixed typo.
setupdb path defaults to ../loki_setupdb, now.
Patched to look for setupdb at ../loki_setupdb by default.
Added -lz which isn't always in the xdelta libs list

Sam Lantinga - Wed May  2 12:08:16 PDT 2001
 * Added --noprompt command line option to update.sh

Sam Lantinga - Tue Apr 10 20:55:44 PDT 2001
 * Added an environment variable LOKI_PATCH_UNSAFE
   - If this is set to "1", then it will use less diskspace for patches,
     but if a patch fails, it will corrupt your installation.
   - If this is set to "2", then not enough diskspace is not fatal.
   - If this is set to "3", then most errors will not stop the patch.

Sam Lantinga - Tue Apr 10 20:17:01 PDT 2001
 * Fixed out of memory condition caused by not properly unmapping files
